{"tid":2513250,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel新劇 <<Ms Marvel>> 穆斯林女主角片場曝光","createTime":"2021-05-02T10:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T11:17:56.000Z","uid":207767,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a6e9232f9ddca65b8666b75b4c869180b2579dd6","tid":2513250,"uid":207767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T10:59:07.000Z","msg":"新劇集《驚奇女士》的片場照曝光，女主角伊曼&middot;維拉尼（Iman Vellani）身穿驚奇女士制服登場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRhs7mhej8E6XiT1SGL2prXt16AXAW1b32Garzi6uJo4k?filename=WZqWCtD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZqWCtD.jpg&h=bfd26383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVyVhMEzRxCoghxe5LyHAfbqRcaLs7DE4mTF1Sfy2yPKk?filename=goZo1Vj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgoZo1Vj.jpg&h=471f2340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmayA1dbpqJfNJoXHAY3DUX7qSaXv1JD2wDMjcfJdW4hD7?filename=9kyxaOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kyxaOE.jpg&h=1a750d13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX3X2MTs72GEypVBfw1xDNx1HPDfSEvp9icPEdRSudDg2?filename=zrOxaOF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzrOxaOF.jpg&h=61a4e70c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdTbdbLbcEMDvfo642JwkAXS7p3ZqVQ4pFihrscjsmPMd?filename=QP5rZG1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQP5rZG1.jpg&h=915628c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本片主角為卡瑪拉&middot;克汗（Kamala Khan），她出生於美國新澤西州的一個穆斯林的家裡，她的家人都是巴基斯坦人。 她擁有超級力量，可以變形或者變換身體部位的大小。 在驚奇隊長卡羅爾的鼓舞下，她將會把自己的能力用來守護故鄉，並且在之後加入復仇者聯盟。 卡瑪拉&middot;克汗也將是MCU中第一位登上銀幕的穆斯林超級英雄。"},{"pid":"9649d2cff2af0d77b7e94044c8128c6c6c4a4d02","tid":2513250,"uid":207767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T10:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Q